{"tid":1696610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到今時今日，連呢啲野都仲未識？","createTime":"2019-11-06T09:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T10:27:42.000Z","uid":278717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d0683b8e068a4d2e6b9f29059649e1ebd7a81a3","tid":1696610,"uid":278717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:17:37.000Z","msg":"大家好，小弟乃法律小薯一名，見識淺薄。不過最近見到有好多手足俾人拉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以決定用我僅有嘅法律知識寫一篇關於被捕後應該要留意嘅事情，希望大家至少有個心理準備，喺唔小心俾人拉咗嘅時候都知道有咩可以做：<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">乜都唔好講</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢樣野法律界嘅師兄師姐們講到口都臭埋，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">大家係有絕對嘅權利保持緘默</span></strong></span>，而咁做係唔會令法庭對你作出不利嘅推定。記得無論任何人，係任何人包括同你一齊被捕嘅人（除咗你嘅律師或者你非常信任嘅家人朋友之外），都<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好同佢講任何野</span></strong></span>，因為佢哋係可以將你講過嘅嘢作為呈堂證供，尤其是可能<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>有popo借機套你料</strong></span>。記住你同popo合作一定唔會有好處㗎！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請律師</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n律師一定要搵，因為佢係你俾人拉嘅時候最好嘅依靠。佢能夠確保你被拘留時受到嘅對待，都得以記錄在案，方便日後上庭嘅時候幫到你。當然，popo依家好有可能會唔跟程序做嘢，但係無論如何都要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">堅持搵律師，同埋保持緘默</span></strong></span>。仲有，當你打電話搵律師嘅時候，一定要<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小心簡潔說話</span></strong></span></strong>，以防隔牆有耳，偷聽你講嘢，因為咁可能會成為證據，對你絕對不利。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">盡量記住被捕時所有發生咗嘅事</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢樣野好重要，因為如果你被捕時popo對你做咗任何對你唔公平嘅事，你係需要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">盡快俾你嘅律師知道</span></strong></span>，並且<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">即場作出投訴</span></strong></span>。咁樣先可以落簿，喺你上庭時由你嘅律師提出，確保你嘅權益得到保障（尤其當你俾人砌生豬肉或者屈打成招嘅時候）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>冷靜應對</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n當popo質問你嘅時候，向林奠學習，冷處理佢哋嘅行為，禮貌地拒絕回應。仲有，唔好講<del><span style=\"color: violet;\">「我唔知」、「我唔想答」</span></del>，因為呢啲說話都代表你作緊供，係可以作為呈堂證供，記住講<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">「我無嘢講」</span></span></strong>就可以。由今日起，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">背熟呢句</span></strong>，等你俾人問都可以好自動咁拒絕回答啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">盡量送醫</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果可行，盡量要求送去醫院。咁樣<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">醫院嘅人可以幫你</span></strong></span>，譬如要求popo俾你通知家人你俾人拉咗，同時popo都唔會夠膽對你做任何野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">善用法援</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n當你要上庭時而你手頭拮据，記得仲有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">當值律師服務</span></span></strong>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">法援</span></strong></span>。除咗星火之外，呢兩樣都可以令你冇財政憂慮去搵律師，所以一定要去申請。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要係，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>隨身帶住律師嘅電話號碼</strong></span></span>，方便你隨時打電話俾律師，尋求法律援助<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>（或者打俾屋企人叫佢哋幫你搵律師）</strong></span></span>。另外，假如你唔記得或者唔見咗個律師電話，要記住popo係有個律師嘅聯絡list俾你打電話搵律師，要好好善用（雖然popo好大機會用藉口唔俾個list你）。當然，寫係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>自己隻手或者唔顯眼嘅地方（可以的話用油性marker）</strong></span></span>，更加可以確保自己唔會唔見個電話號碼。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>以下係一班同路人好努力做出嚟嘅懶人包，值得一看：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkplg.org/category/resources/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkplg.org%2Fcategory%2Fresources%2F&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=36ed059e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkplg.org/category/resources/</a></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，當然希望<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">大家唔好俾人拉</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻煩咁多位手足幫手推呢篇文，等其他手足都可以留個名，得閒溫吓習！！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">復</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">時</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">代</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">革</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">命</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">香港人</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">堅持！</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"dff4ba364fa41ba5459a8810cf8916bdf0820d74","tid":1696610,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:29:33.000Z","msg":"11月9日：7區開花！香港人反抗！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689356\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689356</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"19b1f6a187248d0892da80640ff33018c15c9aaf","tid":1696610,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:30:20.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"d7a348a5dce99ecfec1877013251e6dabd44fef6","tid":1696610,"uid":278717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"推吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}